name: HAUNTING OPPAI
description:
This is my first mint after the end of the Tezo Girls Project. I was just wondering if i would be capable of doing some pokemon art with ecchi stuff all in together.

So, here it is! hahaha. Gengar is my fav Pokémon, but i think Haunter just fit better in this case because of the floating hands xD.

Hope you enjoy!
